a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"912b686f4e9961c110d901f85e95e3f88267b644","tid":1241461,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bb6a09448b1e34f79970bc2f40e3d91a5f2062","tid":1241461,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"325ab8ede4cefac91265967f0c0dbd4a7feba73a","tid":1241461,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0de8490cc4947db5fbfea5bf7a7d26f71c7848fe","tid":1241461,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13441d01902d405ed61229682e0fd7c03056e0b","tid":1241461,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a4d4bbd15e431da3a050ee16da678d4b7c6625","tid":1241461,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"由六月九號103萬人遊行到六月十二號警方使用過分武力大規模清場。警方越做越過份。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我draft左封信，大家過過目。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的都係希望搵多啲人，一人一信對爆聯合國人權專員個email <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請佢地就中國政府、香港政府及香港警察所使用嘅暴力及破壞人權展開獨立調查。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫手，一人一信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人一信,寄俾聯合國人權專員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221849</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"0d79052ac96402f3dfc80bb2926a187c5e742695","tid":1241461,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05532dd131856c5dff869c0f7109c9973ab11e22","tid":1241461,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a423ba6d5c7e271d1c620a2b8dfbb3cf17b6ff65","tid":1241461,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8bb6abcfc12de84766b48287a07c056ef248a7","tid":1241461,"uid":255373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4741a89fd91ee5ebba72e4c27c2023f6cb6d3ba","tid":1241461,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f0f86cb82facd9232a3c9000e1480d396dab1a3","tid":1241461,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n6.19  宗教界都幫手製造輿論壓力 又指行動升級會為留守者作心靈支援<br />\n連登仔 香港人 唔好又錯過機會 <br />\n</span><br />\n宗教界再次發聲 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243792</a>"},{"pid":"70c99e9a2e799c65908ebe3f60cb93142d1dab95","tid":1241461,"uid":180663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:22:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b037bd3594675471ee63ce77a8e2b455a7fd426a","tid":1241461,"uid":112221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T21:08:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ae4110dcfffac8cfb21fae8c8e28dc6ec334427","tid":1241461,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"